title: Europa League: When is the round of 16 draw? When will the games take place? Who's in it?
text:
Europa League: When is the round of 16 draw? When will the games take place? Who's in it? MANCHESTER UNITED cruised into the Europa League round of 16 - but when is the draw? PUBLISHED: 18:56, Wed, Feb 22, 2017 | UPDATED: 19:00, Wed, Feb 22, 2017 AFP/GETTY Jose Mourinho's side moved into the next round of the Europa League 
Manchester United overcame St Etienne with a 4-0 aggregate win after two legs, but who could they face in the next round? When is the draw? 
The Europa League round of 16 draw takes place at 13:00CET on Friday. 
It will be streamed live on the UEFA website. When will the games take place? 
Games will be played on Thursday 9 and 16 March at 19:00CET and 21:05CET, with the exact schedule to be confirmed after the draw. 
The teams drawn first will be at home in the first legs. Man United player ratings against Saint-Etienne Wed, February 22, 2017
